    • Method Detail

      • setFacility

        public ALBStreamingSyslogConfig.Builder setFacility(java.lang.Long facility)
        Facility value, as defined in RFC5424, must be between 0 and 23 inclusive. Allowed values are 0-23. Default value when not specified in API or module is interpreted by ALB Controller as 16. format: int64
        Parameters:
        facility - New value for the property.

      • setFilteredLogSeverity

        public ALBStreamingSyslogConfig.Builder setFilteredLogSeverity(java.lang.Long filteredLogSeverity)
        Severity code, as defined in RFC5424, for filtered logs. This must be between 0 and 7 inclusive. Allowed values are 0-7. Default value when not specified in API or module is interpreted by ALB Controller as 5. format: int64
        Parameters:
        filteredLogSeverity - New value for the property.

      • setHostname

        public ALBStreamingSyslogConfig.Builder setHostname(java.lang.String hostname)
        String to use as the hostname in the syslog messages. This string can contain only printable ASCII characters (hex 21 to hex 7E; no space allowed). Default value when not specified in API or module is interpreted by ALB Controller as AviVantage.
        Parameters:
        hostname - New value for the property.

      • setNonSignificantLogSeverity

        public ALBStreamingSyslogConfig.Builder setNonSignificantLogSeverity(java.lang.Long nonSignificantLogSeverity)
        Severity code, as defined in RFC5424, for non-significant logs. This must be between 0 and 7 inclusive. Allowed values are 0-7. Default value when not specified in API or module is interpreted by ALB Controller as 6. format: int64
        Parameters:
        nonSignificantLogSeverity - New value for the property.

      • setSignificantLogSeverity

        public ALBStreamingSyslogConfig.Builder setSignificantLogSeverity(java.lang.Long significantLogSeverity)
        Severity code, as defined in RFC5424, for significant logs. This must be between 0 and 7 inclusive. Allowed values are 0-7. Default value when not specified in API or module is interpreted by ALB Controller as 4. format: int64
        Parameters:
        significantLogSeverity - New value for the property.
